git clone https://github.com/varadharaj213/PET-Adoption.git



To run backend: 

installation -->>

cd backend
npm init -y 
npm install express mongoose cors bcrypt razorpay shorted
npm install express-session

to run -->>
node server.js


frontend: 

cd frontend 
npxhttp-server

open browser with url:
http://127.0.0.1:8080/login.html



?? if you no need captcha in the login page just add false in this key in login.html ??
const USE_CAPTCHA = false;